\id REV - Biblica® Open New Luo Translation 2020 
\h Fweny 
\toc1 Fweny 
\toc2 Fweny 
\toc3 Fwe 
\mt1 Fweny 
\c 1  
\s1 Weche motelo 
\p  
\v 1 Ma e fweny ma Nyasaye nomiyo Yesu Kristo mondo onyisgo jotichne gik manyaka timre mapiyo. Kristo nomiyo fwenyni ongʼere ka nooro malaikane mondo onyis Johana jatichne.  
\v 2 Johana nyiso gigo duto mane oneno e fweny ma en wach Nyasaye kod weche duto mane Yesu Kristo owacho.  
\v 3 Ngʼatno masomo weche mokorgi en jahawi kendo ogwedh jogo mawinjo wechegi kendo kano weche mondikgi e chunygi, nikech kinde ma gigi biro timoree chiegni. 
\b  
\s1 Mos kod pak 
\p  
\v 4 An Johana, 
\b  
\p Andiko ni kanise abiriyo manie piny Asia: 
\b  
\p Ngʼwono kod kwe obednu koa kuom Jal mantie, Jal mane nitie kendo Jal mabiro betie, kendo koa kuom Roho abiriyo manie nyim kom duongʼne,  
\v 5 kendo moa kuom Yesu Kristo, ma janeno mar adier ma ok lokre, jal mane okwongo chier oa kuom joma otho, jaloch mar ruodhi manie piny. 
\b  
\b  
\p Ne Jal moherowa kendo mosegonyowa kuom richowa gi rembe,  
\v 6 mi osemiyo wadoko oganda mag pinyruodhi kod jodolo matiyone Nyasache kendo Wuon mare kendo wuon-gi, mad duongʼ odogne manyaka chiengʼ! Amin. 
\q1  
\v 7 “Neuru, obiro gi boche polo,”\f + \fr 1:7 \ft \xt Dan 7:13\f* 
\q2 kendo “wenge duto nonene, 
\q1 nyaka jogo mane ochwowe gi tongʼ”; 
\q2 kendo ogendini duto “manie piny noywagre nikech en.”\f + \fr 1:7 \ft \xt Zek 12:10\f* 
\qc Mano e kaka enobedi! Amin. 
\p  
\v 8 Ruoth Nyasaye wacho niya, “An e Alfa gi Omega, tiende ni Chakruok kendo Giko, Jal mantie, Jal mane nitie, kendo Jal mabiro betie, Jehova Nyasaye Maratego.” 
\b  
\s1 Johana oneno ngʼat machalo gi Wuod Dhano 
\p  
\v 9 An Johana ma owadu, ma bende achiel kodu e sand gi pinyruoth kod dhil e kinda marwa kuom Yesu, ne an e chula mar Fatimo nikech wach Nyasaye, kod timo neno kuom Yesu.  
\v 10 E odiechieng Ruoth, ne an kuom Roho, ne awinjo dwol maduongʼ makok ka turumbete yo kangʼeya.  
\v 11 Kowacho niya, \wj “Ndik gik moko duto mineno e kitabu kendo orgi ne kanise abiriyogi: Efeso, gi Smurna, gi Pergamo, gi Thuatira, gi Sarde gi Filadelfia kod Laodikia.”\wj* 
\p  
\v 12 Eka nalokora mondo ane ngʼat mane wuoyo koda. Kane alokora ne aneno rachungi teyni abiriyo mag dhahabu,  
\v 13 to e dier rachungi teynigo ne nitie ngʼato machalo gi wuod dhano\f + \fr 1:13 \ft \xt Dan 7:13\f* morwakore gi kandho mochopo nyaka e tiende piny, kendo kotweyo kore gi okanda mar dhahabu.  
\v 14 Yie wiye ne rachar ka yie rombo, bende ne rachar ka pe, to wengene ne chalo gi mach makakni.  
\v 15 Tiendene ne pakni ka mula mopwodhi gi mach, bende dwonde ne mor ka pi mopongʼ mawuo.  
\v 16 E lwete ma korachwich notingʼo sulwe abiriyo, bende ligangla mabith ma dhoge ariyo ne wuok e dhoge. Lela wangʼe ne rieny ka chiengʼ marieny mangʼangʼni. 
\p  
\v 17 Kane anene, ne apodho e tiende mana ka ngʼat motho. Eka noketo lwete ma korachwich kuoma mowachona niya, \wj “Kik iluor. An e Jal Mokwongo kendo Jal Mogik.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj An e Jal Mangima; ne atho, to koro angima nyaka chiengʼ! An-gi rayaw mar tho kod mar piny joma otho.\wj* 
\p  
\v 19 \wj “Kuom mano, ndik gigo miseneno, gigo mantie kod gigo mabiro timore e kindego mabiro.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Tiend wach mopandi mar sulwe abiriyo mane ineno e lweta ma korachwich, kod rachungi teyni abiriyogo mag dhahabu ema: Sulwe abiriyogo e malaike mag kanise abiriyo, to rachungi teyni abiriyo gin e kanise abiriyogo.\wj* 
\c 2  
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Efeso 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Efeso kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche Jal motingʼo sulwe abiriyo e lwete korachwich kendo mawuotho e kind rachungi teyni abiriyo mag dhahabu:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 2 \wj Angʼeyo timbeni gi tichni matek kod kinda mari. Angʼeyo ni isetiyo matek kendo isetimo kinda. Angʼeyo ni imon gi joma timo timbe mamono. Angʼeyo ni isetemo joma luongore ni joote, to ok gin joote, ma iyudo ni gin jo-miriambo.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Isetimo kinda kendo isehori e bwo chandruok nikech nyinga, to ok iseol.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 4 \wj To kata kamano an kodi gi wach; iseweyo hera mane iherago mokwongo.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Omiyo parie bor mar kuma iseaye ka ipodho! Lokri iwe richo mondo itim gik mane itimo mokwongo. To ka ok ilokori to abiro biro mi agol tachi kare.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj To kata kamano nitie tim maber ma apwoyigo, to isin gi timbe maricho mag jo-Nikolao ma an bende asin-go.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 7 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ne kanisa. Ngʼat molocho to anami adiera mar chamo olemb yadh ngima manie puotho mar Nyasaye.\wj* 
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Smurna 
\p  
\v 8 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Smurna kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche mag Jal Mokwongo kendo Mogik, Jal mane otho kendo ochier.\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 9 \wj Angʼeyo chandruokni kod dhierni to kata kamano in jamoko. Bende angʼeyo ayany ma joma wuondore ni jo-Yahudi yanyigo to gin mana joma lamo Satan.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Kik iluor kuom sand ma ibiro yudo machiegni. Adier, anyisou ni Jachien biro tweyo jomoko kuomu e od twech mondo otemugo kendo ubiro yudo sandruok kuom ndalo apar. Bed ja-adiera nyaka kar tho mi anamiyi osimbo mar ngima.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 11 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa. Ngʼat molocho to tho mar ariyo ok notime gimoro kata matin.\wj* 
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Pergamo 
\p  
\v 12 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Pergamo kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche Jal man-gi ligangla mabith ma dhoge ariyo:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 13 \wj Angʼeyo kama idakie. En kama kom duongʼ mar Satan nitie to kata kamano isebedo kirito nyinga ahinya. Bende ne ok ikwedo yie miyiego kuoma, kata mana e kinde mane Antipa janeno mara mar adier onegi e dalau kama Satan odakie.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 14 \wj To kata kamano an kod weche matin kuomi: In kod jomoko kanyo maluwo puonj mar Balaam mane opuonjo Balak kaka onyalo ywayo jo-Israel mondo otim richo ka gichamo chiemo motimgo misango ni nyiseche manono kendo kuom richo mar chode.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj To bende in kod jomoko maluwo puonj mag jo-Nikolao.\wj* 
\v 16 \wj Emomiyo lokri iwe richo! Nikech ka ok ilokori to abiro biro mapiyo mondo aked kodgi gi ligangla mawuok e dhoga.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 17 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa. Ngʼat molocho abiro miyo manna moko mopandi. Bende abiro miye kidi marachar mondikie nying manyien maonge ngʼat mongʼeyo makmana ngʼat monwangʼe.\wj* 
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Thuatira 
\p  
\v 18 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Thuatira kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche mag Wuod Nyasaye ma wengene chalo gi mach makakni bende tiendene chal ka mula mapakni.\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 19 \wj Angʼeyo timbeni gi herani kod yie mari gi tiji mar konyo ji kod kindani. Kendo imedo tiyo maber moloyo kaka nitiyo mokwongo.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 20 \wj Kata kamano, an kodi gi wach moro ma ok ber kuomi; iyie gi dhako miluongo ni Jezebel maluongore ni janabi madhako. En ema omiyo jotichna lal kopuonjogi mondo giterre, kendo mondo gicham chiemo motimgo misango ni nyiseche manono.\wj* 
\v 21 \wj Ne amiye kinde mondo olokre owe richo mar chode to notamore.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Omiyo abiro bole e kitanda mar thagruok bende abiro miyo joma terore kode yudo thagruok malich ka ok giyie loko chunygi mi giweyo timo richo.\wj* 
\v 23 \wj Nyithinde bende abiro nego, mi kanise biro ngʼeyo ni An ema angʼeyo chunje gi paro mag ji bende ni anapog ngʼato ka ngʼato kaka tichne chalo.\wj* 
\v 24 \wj To Koro un ji mamoko duto modongʼ man Thuatira ma ok oseluwo puonjne kendo mapok ongʼeyo gima jomoko luongo ni weche mopondo mag Satan, ‘Ok aketnu tingʼ moro mapek,\wj* 
\v 25 \wj omiyo makmana gima in-go matek nyaka abi.’\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 26 \wj To ngʼat molocho kendo timo dwarona nyaka giko, abiro miyo loch kuom ogendini.\wj* 
\qm1  
\v 27 \wj ‘Ngʼat molochono norit ogendini gi ludh nyinyo,\wj* 
\qm2 \wj kendo notogi matindo tindo\wj* 
\qm2 \wj ka ngʼama toyo agulu,’\wj*\f + \fr 2:27 \ft \xt Zab 2:9\f* 
\mi \wj mana kaka Wuora osemiya teko mar loch.\wj* 
\v 28 \wj To anamiye sulwe mar okinyi.\wj* 
\v 29 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa.\wj* 
\c 3  
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Sarde 
\p  
\v 1 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Sarde kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche mag Jal motingʼo Roho abiriyo mag Nyasaye kod sulwe abiriyo.\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Angʼeyo timbeni; kendo kaka igeno ni in gi nying ni ingima to adiera isetho.\wj* 
\v 2 \wj Omiyo chiew! Mondo ijiw gima pod odongʼno kapok otho chuth, nimar timbeni ayudo korem e nyim Nyasaye.\wj* 
\v 3 \wj Emomiyo par ane gik mane opuonji kendo mane isewinjo, makgi kendo lokri iwe richo. Ka ok ichiew to abiro biro apoya mana kaka jakuo ma ok ibi ngʼeyo sa ma anabiyee iri.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 4 \wj Kata kamano nitie jomoko manok e dala mar Sarde ma ok osechido lepgi. Gin to gini wuothi koda ka girwakore gi lewni marochere nikech gin joma owinjore.\wj* 
\v 5 \wj Ngʼat molocho bende norwakre gi lewni marochere kaka gin, bende ok naruch nyinge e kitap ngima, to abiro hulo nyinge e nyim Wuora gi Malaike mage.\wj* 
\v 6 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa.\wj* 
\s1 Wach moter ne kanisa man Filadelfia 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Ndik ne Malaika morito kanisa man Filadelfia kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche mag Jal maler kendo ma ja-adiera, motingʼo kifungu mar Daudi. Gima oyawo to onge ngʼama nyalo loro; kendo gima oloro to onge ngʼama nyalo yawo.\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 8 \wj Angʼeyo timbeni. Omiyo aseyawoni dhoot kendo onge ngʼama nyalo lore. Angʼeyo ni in giteko matin to kata kamano iserito wachna bende ok isekweda.\wj* 
\v 9 \wj Abiro miyo joma lamo Satan, maluongore ni gin jo-Yahudi to ok gin. Jogi gin jomiriambo. Abiro chunogi mondo gipodhi e tiendu eka gingʼe ni aherou.\wj* 
\v 10 \wj Nikech iserito chikna ka ihoyori mos kuom masira, abiro riti maber e ndalo mar masira mabiro yudo piny duto mondo otemgo joma odak e piny.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 11 \wj Abiro biro piyo. Omiyo mak matek gima in-go mondo kik ngʼato mayi osimboni.\wj* 
\v 12 \wj Ngʼat molocho anami obed siro e hekalu mar Nyasacha. Ok enochak owuog kanyo. Anandik nying Nyasacha kuome bende anandik nying dala mar Nyasacha ma en Jerusalem manyien, mabiro aa e polo kuom Nyasacha kendo abiro ndiko nyinga maler kuome.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa.\wj* 
\s1 Wach moter ni kanisa man Laudikia 
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Ndik ne malaika morito kanisa man Laodikia kama:\wj* 
\b  
\pi1 \wj Magi e weche moa kuom Jal miluongo ni Amin, Jal ma ja-adiera kendo janeno ma Ja-ratiro, Jalno ma jaloch kuom chwech duto mag Nyasaye.\wj* 
\b  
\pi1  
\v 15 \wj Angʼeyo timbeni ni ok ingʼich bende ok iliet. Dine ber kibedo maliet kata mangʼich!\wj* 
\v 16 \wj To nikech koro indhem-ndhem, ok iliet bende ok ingʼich, abiro ngʼogi oko.\wj* 
\v 17 \wj Iwacho ni, ‘An jamoko; kendo ni aseyudo mwandu mathoth bende onge gima achando.’ To ok ingʼeyo ni in ngʼat mathagore mogik; idhier, in ngʼat monego okechi; bende in muofu kendo in duk.\wj* 
\v 18 \wj To angʼadoni rieko mondo ibi ingʼiew kuoma dhahabu mopwodhi gi mach mondo ibed jamoko. Ngʼiew lewni marochere kuoma mondo irwakrigo oumni dugi makeloni wichkuot. Ngʼiew yath kuoma mondo ithiedh-go wangʼi mondo inen.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 19 \wj Joma ahero ema akwero kendo akumo. Omiyo bed ja-adiera kendo ilok chunyi iwe timo richo.\wj* 
\v 20 \wj Ne! Achungʼ e dhoot kendo aduongʼo, ka ngʼato angʼata owinjo dwonda mi oyawona dhoot to abiro donjo ire mi achiem kode to en bende ochiem koda.\wj* 
\pi1  
\v 21 \wj Ngʼat molocho anami thuolo mar bedo koda e kom duongʼna mana kaka an bende kane aselocho ne abedo gi wuora e kom duongʼne.\wj* 
\v 22 \wj Ngʼat man-gi it mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanisa.”\wj* 
\c 4  
\s1 Kom duongʼ manie polo 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼe ne angʼicho mi aneno dhoot moyaw e polo. To dwol machalo gi turumbete mane asewinjo mokwongo kawuoyo koda cha nowachona niya, \wj “Bi malo ka mondo anyisi gik mabiro timore bangʼ wechegi.”\wj* 
\v 2 Roho nopongʼa mana gisano mi aneno kom duongʼ e polo ka ngʼato obetie.  
\v 3 Ngʼat mane obetie komno ne kite nenore ka kite ma nengogi tek miluongo ni jaspa gi sardus. Kit lihudu mar koth man-gi kido machalo emerald ne olworo kom duongʼno.  
\v 4 Kom duongʼno ne olwor gi kombe moko piero ariyo gangʼwen ma jodongo piero ariyo gangʼwen obedoe. Ne girwakore gi lewni marochere to e wigi negirwake osimbe mag dhahabu.  
\v 5 Polo ne mil kendo mor kariadore koa e kom duongʼno, E nyim kom duongʼno ne nitie teyni abiriyo maliel. Magi e roho abiriyo mag Nyasaye.  
\v 6 Bende e nyim kom duongʼno ne nitie gimoro manenore ka nam machalo gi kio mar rangʼi, to orieny ka pi. 
\p E dier komno tir gi alworane ne nitie gik moko angʼwen mangima man-gi wenge mangʼeny yo ka nyimgi kod yo ka tokgi.  
\v 7 Gima ngima mokwongo ne chalo gi sibuor, mar ariyo ne chalo gi nyarwath, mar adek ne lela wangʼe chalo gi mar dhano, to mar angʼwen ne chalo gi ongo mafuyo.  
\v 8 Moro ka moro kuom gik mangimago ne nigi bwombe auchiel kendo ne gin gi wenge mathoth molworo dendgi nyaka e bwo bwombegi. Odiechiengʼ gi otieno duto negisiko kagiwacho niya, 
\qc “ ‘Mano kaka Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego Ler! 
\qc Oler adier! Yaye Mano kaka oler.’\f + \fr 4:8 \ft \xt Isa 6:3\f* 
\qc En e Jal mane nitie, kendo Jal mantie, kendo Jal mabiro betie.” 
\m  
\v 9 E seche duto ka gik mangimago nedwoko erokamano ka gipako kendo puoyo Jal mane obedo e kom duongʼ kendo mangima nyaka chiengʼ;  
\v 10 to jodongo piero ariyo gangʼwen-go ne podho e nyim ngʼat mobet e kom duongʼ ka gilamo Jal Mantie nyaka chiengʼ. Negibolo osimbegi e nyim kom duongʼ kagiwacho niya: 
\q1  
\v 11 “Yaye Ruodhwa kendo Nyasachwa, 
\q2 iwinjori yudo duongʼ gi pak kod teko, 
\q1 nimar nichweyo gik moko duto, 
\q2 kendo kuom dwaroni ne ochwegi, 
\q2 kendo gibedo mangima.” 
\c 5  
\s1 Kitabu kod nyarombo 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne aneno kitabu ma jal mane obet e kom duongʼ otingʼo e lwete ma korachwich, kitabuno ne ondiki iye koni gi koni kendo ne odine gi kido abiriyo motweye.  
\v 2 Eka ne aneno malaika maratego kalando gi dwol maduongʼ niya, “Ere ngʼama owinjore gonyo kidogi mondo oel kitabuni?”  
\v 3 To ne ok oyudi ngʼato angʼata e polo kata e piny mane nyalo elo kitabuno, kata mane nyalo rango iye.  
\v 4 Kuom mano ne aywak malit nikech ne onge ngʼama nyalo elo kitabuno mondo onyiswa gima ondiki e iye.  
\v 5 To achiel kuom Jodongogo nowachona niya, “We ywak! Nikech Sibuor moa e dhood Juda ma Nyakwar Daudi ema oselocho kendo en ema owinjore elo kitabu modin gi kido abiriyogo.” 
\p  
\v 6 Eka ne aneno Nyarombo machalo ka gima ne osenegi kochungo e dier kom duongʼ, kolwore gi gik mangima angʼwen kod jodongo. Ne en gi tunge abiriyo gi wenge abiriyo ma gin Roho abiriyo mag Nyasaye moseor e piny mangima.  
\v 7 Nobiro mi okawo kitabuno e lwedo korachwich mar Jalno mane obedo e kom duongʼ.  
\v 8 E sa mane okawoe kitabuno gik mangima angʼwen ka gi Jodongo piero ariyo gangʼwen-go ne opodho auma e nyim Nyarombo. Moro ka moro kuomgi ne nigi nyatiti kod tewni mag dhahabu ma ubani opongʼo. Tewni mag ubanigo ochungʼ kar lemo mar jomaler.  
\v 9 Kendo ne giwero wer manyien, kagiwacho niya: 
\q1 “In ema iwinjori kawo kitabuni, 
\q2 kendo gonyo kido molorego, 
\q1 nikech in ema nonegi 
\q2 kendo rembi ne ingʼiewogo ji ni Nyasaye, 
\q2 koa e dhoudi duto, kendo mawacho dhok duto kod pinje duto. 
\q1  
\v 10 Isemiyo gibedo oganda mag pinyruodhi kendo jodolo mondo giti ne Nyasachwa, 
\q2 kendo ginibed joloch e piny.” 
\p  
\v 11 Eka ne angʼicho, kendo nawinjo dwond malaike mangʼeny ma kwan-gi ne romo gana gi gana kendo tara gi tara. Negilworo kom duongʼ kaachiel gi gik mangimago kod Jodongo.  
\v 12 Ne giwer gi dwol maduongʼ niya: 
\q1 “Duongʼ obed ni Nyarombo manonegi, 
\q2 mondo oyud loch gi mwandu, gi rieko gi luor, 
\q2 gi duongʼ kod pak.” 
\p  
\v 13 Eka nawinjo ka gik mangima duto manie polo kendo e piny kod e bwo piny, kendo e nam, kendo gigo duto mochwe modak eigi, kawer niya: 
\q1 “Pak gi duongʼ kod loch obed ni Jal mobet e kom duongʼ 
\q2 gi Nyarombo manyaka chiengʼ!” 
\m  
\v 14 Kendo gik mangima angʼwen-go nowacho niya “Amin” eka jodongogo nopodho piny mi gidende. 
\c 6  
\s1 Kido modin-go kitabu 
\p  
\v 1 Eka naneno Nyarombo ka elo achiel kuom kido abiriyogo. Nawinjo dwond achiel kuom gik mangima angʼwen-go kaluongo gi dwol machalo ka mor polo, kawacho niya; “Bi!”  
\v 2 Ne angʼicho mi aneno faras marachar. Ngʼat moidhe ne otingʼo atungʼ kendo ne osidhne osimbo. Ne owuok gi farase ka jaloch madhi mondo olochi. 
\p  
\v 3 Kane Nyarombo noketho kido mar ariyo, ne awinjo gima ngima mar ariyo kaluongo niya, “Bi!”  
\v 4 Eka faras machielo ma silwal nobiro. Ngʼat moidhe ne omi teko mondo ogol kwe e piny, mondo ji onegre kendgi. Ngʼatno nomi ligangla maduongʼ! 
\p  
\v 5 Kane Nyarombo noketho kido mar adek, ne awinjo gima ngima mar adek kawacho niya, “Bi!” Ne angʼicho to e nyima kanyo ne nitie faras maratengʼ! Ngʼat moidhe ne otingʼo ratil e lwete.  
\v 6 Ne awinjo gima chalo gi dwol e dier gik mangima angʼwen-go kawacho niya, “Koro gorogoro mar ngano ibiro ngʼiew gi nengo maromre gi chudo michulo jatich e odiechiengʼ achiel kendo gorogoro adek mar shairi bende chal gi chudono, to nengo mo zeituni gi divai kik medi.” 
\p  
\v 7 Ka Nyarombo noketho kido mar angʼwen, nawinjo dwond gima ngima mar angʼwen kaluongo niya, “Bi!”  
\v 8 Nangʼicho to ne aneno faras marabuor e nyima! Ngʼat moidhe niluongo ni Tho, to piny joma otho ne luwo bangʼe machiegni. Ne omigi teko kuom bath piny moromo achiel kuom angʼwen mondo gimi lweny kata kech kata dera kata tuoche kata ondiegi maricho mag bungu mondo gineg ji. 
\p  
\v 9 Kane oketho kido mar abich, ne aneno chunje jomoko mane osenegi ka nitie e bwo kendo mar misango nikech Wach Nyasaye kendo nikech neno mane gisiko gihulo.  
\v 10 Eka ne giywak gi dwol maduongʼ niya, “Nyaka karangʼo ma ibiro ngʼado bura ni joma odak e piny ka ichulo kuor kuom rembwa, yaye Ruoth Manyalo Gik Moko Duto, in miler kendo ja-adiera?”  
\v 11 Eka ngʼato ka ngʼato kuomgi nomi kandho marachar, kendo nowachnigi ni mondo girit kuom kinde matin, nyaka kwan mar jotich wetegi kod jowetegi mibiro nego kaka ne oneg-gi orom. 
\p  
\v 12 Ne angʼicho kane oyawo kido mar auchiel. Piny noyiengni matek. Mi wangʼ chiengʼ nolokore maratengʼ ti, machal gi lep gugru mirwako e kuyo molos gi yie diel, dwe bende nolokore makwar ka remo;  
\v 13 kendo sulwe manie polo nolwar e piny mana kaka olemo mag ngʼowu mapok ochiek lwar koa kuom yadhe ka yamo mager kudho.  
\v 14 Polo nolal nono ka kitabu mibano kendo gode duto gi chula duto nogol oa kuonde mane gintie. 
\p  
\v 15 Eka ruodhi mag piny, gi ji madongo, kod jotelo mag lweny, gi jo-mwandu, kod joma roteke, kaachiel gi ji duto ma wasumbini, gi joma ni thuolo, giduto ne gipondo e rogo kendo e bwo lwendni mag gode.  
\v 16 Negiluongo gode gi lwendini kagiwacho niya, “Podhuru kuomwa mondo uumwa kupandowa ni wangʼ Jal mobet e kom duongʼno, kendo ne mirimb Nyarombo!  
\v 17 Nikech chiengʼ maduongʼ mar mirimb Nyasaye osechopo, to en ngʼama nyalo chungʼ mondo osire.” 
\c 7  
\s1 Ji alufu mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen moyier 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼe ne aneno malaike angʼwen kochungʼ e tunge angʼwen mag piny, ka gimako yembe angʼwen mag piny, mondo gigengʼ yamo kik kudhi e piny kata e nam kata e yath moro amora.  
\v 2 Eka naneno malaika machielo kalor piny kowuok yo wuok chiengʼ, kotingʼo gima igoyogo kido mar Nyasaye mangima. Noluongo malaike angʼwen mane osemi teko mondo ohiny piny kod nam gi dwol maduongʼ.  
\v 3 Nowachonigi, “Kik uhiny piny, kata nam, kata yiende nyaka chop waket kido e lela wangʼ jotich Nyasachwa.”  
\v 4 Bangʼe nawinjo kar kwan joma ne oketnegi kido, ne gin ji alufu mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen (144,000) mowuok e dhout Israel duto. 
\b  
\li1  
\v 5 Koa e dhood Juda nowal ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 koa e dhood Reuben ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa e dhood Gad ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1  
\v 6 Koa e dhood Asher ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa dhood Naftali ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa dhood Manase ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1  
\v 7 Koa dhood Simeon ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa dhood Lawi ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa dhood Isakar ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1  
\v 8 Koa dhood Zebulun ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 Koa dhood Josef ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000), 
\li1 kendo dhood Benjamin ji alufu apar gariyo (12,000). 
\s1 Oganda maduongʼ morwakore gi kandho marochere 
\p  
\v 9 Bangʼ mani ne angʼicho, mi naneno oganda mar ji mangʼeny ma ok kwanre moa e pinje duto gi dhoudi kod ogendini kod dhok duto kochungo e nyim kom duongʼ, kendo e nyim Nyarombo. Negirwako kandhe marochere bende negitingʼo othidhe e lwetgi.  
\v 10 Ne giywak giduol maduongʼ kagiwacho niya, 
\q1 “Warruok oa kuom Nyasachwa 
\q1 mobedo e kom duongʼ mar loch 
\q1 kendo oa kuom Nyarombo.” 
\m  
\v 11 Malaike duto nochungʼ kolworo kom duongʼ kendo kolworo jodongo kod gik mangima angʼwen. Negikulore piny e nyim kom duongʼ mine gidendo Nyasaye.  
\v 12 Kagiwacho niya, 
\q1 “Amin! 
\q1 Pak gi duongʼ 
\q1 kod rieko gi erokamano gi luor 
\q1 kod teko gi nyalo 
\q1 obed ni Nyasachwa, nyaka chiengʼ. 
\q1 Amin!” 
\p  
\v 13 Eka achiel kuom jodongogo nopenja niya, “Joma orwakore gi lewni marocheregi gin ngʼa gini, to gia kanye?” 
\p  
\v 14 An to nadwoke niya, “Jaduongʼ in ema ingʼeyo, an ok angʼeyo.” 
\p Eka nowachona niya, “Jogi e joma owuok koa e sand mager; giselwoko kandhegi matar gi remb Nyarombo.  
\v 15 Ma emomiyo, 
\q1 “koro gin e nyim kom duongʼ mar Nyasaye, 
\q2 ka gitiyone odiechiengʼ gi otieno ei hekalune; 
\q1 to Jalno mobet e kom duongʼ 
\q2 noumgi korieyo hema mare kuomgi. 
\q1  
\v 16 Kech ok nokagi ngangʼ 
\q2 kendo bende kata riyo ok nomak gi kendo. 
\q1 Liet mar wangʼ chiengʼ ok norieny kuomgi 
\q2 kata liet moro mager ok nowangʼ-gi. 
\q1  
\v 17 Nimar Nyarombo mobedo e kom loch mar Nyasaye nobed jakwadhgi; 
\q2 notelnigi koterogi e sokni mag pi ngima, 
\q1 to Nyasaye noywe pi wangʼ-gi duto.”\f + \fr 7:17 \ft \xt Isa 49:10; 25:8\f* 
\c 8  
\s1 Kido mar abiriyo gi tap wangʼo ubani molos gi dhahabu 
\p  
\v 1 Kane oketho kido mar abiriyo, polo nolingʼ thi kuom kinde ma dirom nus sa. 
\p  
\v 2 Eka naneno malaike abiriyo mochungo e nyim Nyasaye, kendo nomigi turumbete abiriyo. 
\p  
\v 3 Malaika moro machielo nobiro mochungo but kendo mar misango, kotingʼo tap ubani mar dhahabu. Nomiye ubani mangʼeny, kaluwore gi lemo mar jomaler duto, mondo ochiw ewi kendo mar misango molos gi dhahabu manie nyim kom duongʼ.  
\v 4 Iro mar ubani motingʼo lamo mag jomaler nodum kadhi malo e nyim Nyasaye koa e lwet malaika.  
\v 5 Bangʼe malaika nokawo tap ubani, mi opongʼo gi mach moa e kendo mar misango, eka nobole e piny. Bangʼ mano polo nomil malich kariadore matek ka mor, kendo piny noyiengni. 
\s1 Turumbete 
\p  
\v 6 Eka malaike abiriyo mane nigi turumbete abiriyogo ne oikore goyogi. 
\p  
\v 7 Malaika mokwongo nogoyo turumbetene, to pe gi mach mokikore gi remo ema ne owuok, kendo nopuk e piny. To bath piny moromo achiel kuom adek nowangʼ, kendo achiel kuom adek mar yien bende maromo kamano nowangʼ gi lum mangʼich duto nowangʼ. 
\p  
\v 8 Malaika mar ariyo nogoyo turumbetene, mi gima chalo gi got maduongʼ, maliel gi mach, nowiti e nam. To bath nam moromo achiel kuom adek nolokore remo,  
\v 9 momiyo achiel kuom adek mar gik mangima manie nam notho, kendo achiel kuom adek mar yiedhi manie nam nokethi. 
\p  
\v 10 Eka malaika mar adek nogoyo turumbetene mi sulwe maduongʼ maliel ka toch nolwar oa e polo, nolwar kuom achiel mar adek mag aore, kendo kuom sokni duto.  
\v 11 Nying sulweno en, “Gima Kech,” kamano bende achiel kuom adek mar pi nolokore makech, kendo pige makechgo nomiyo ji mangʼeny otho. 
\p  
\v 12 Kendo malaika mar angʼwen nogoyo turumbetene, mi achiel kuom adek mar chiengʼ gi achiel kuom adek mar dwe, kod mar sulwe, notimo mudho, to achiel kuom adek mar odiechiengʼ gi otieno bende notimo mudho. 
\p  
\v 13 Bangʼe nangʼicho mi awinjo ongo mafuyo e kor polo kaywak matek niya, “Lit! Lit! Lit ni joma odak e piny, nikech turumbete modongʼ ma malaike adek biro goyo!” 
\c 9  
\p  
\v 1 Eka malaika mar abich nogoyo turumbete, mine aneno sulwe moro mane oselwar e piny koa e polo. Sulweno ne omi kifungu mar bur matut maonge gikone.  
\v 2 Kane oyawo burno, iro nowuokie machalo gi ich mach maduongʼ. Iro moa e burno noimo chiengʼ kod boche polo molokore maratengʼ.  
\v 3 Kendo bonyo nowuok e yirono mopiyo e piny, to nomigi teko machalo gi teko thomoni manie piny.  
\v 4 To nokwergi ni kik giketh lum manie piny kata gimoro mangʼich kata yien, to ginyalo mana hinyo jogo maonge gi kido mar Nyasaye e lela wengegi.  
\v 5 Ne ok omigi teko mar negogi to nomigi thuolo mar sandogi kuom dweche abich. To rem mane jogo oyudo ne chalgi mano miyudo ka thomoni okayo dhano.  
\v 6 E ndalogo ji nodwar tho, to ok giniyude; ginigomb mondo githo to tho noring-gi aringa. 
\p  
\v 7 Bonyogo ne chalo gi farese moikore ni lweny. E wigi negirwako gik machalo gi osimbo mag dhahabu, to lend wangʼ-gi ne chalo gi lela wangʼ dhano.  
\v 8 Yie wigi ne chalo gi yie wi mon, kendo lekegi ne chalo gi leke sibuoche.  
\v 9 Negirwako gige lweny mag akor machalo gi akor mar nyinyo, to bwombegi ne goyo koko mana ka farese mangʼeny kendo ka geche miywayo kadhi e lweny.  
\v 10 Ne gin gi iwgi makecho kaka thomoni kecho, to e iwgigo ne gin gi teko mar sando kagikayogo ji kuom dweche abich.  
\v 11 Ruodhgi motelo nigi en malaika mar bur matut maonge gikone ma nyinge miluongego gi dho jo-Hibrania en Abadon, to gi dho jo-Yunani en Apoluon (tiende ni Ngʼat maketho gik moko). 
\p  
\v 12 Masira mokwongo osekadho, to masiche ariyo mamoko pod biro. 
\p  
\v 13 Bangʼ mano malaika mar auchiel nogoyo turumbetene, mi nawinjo dwol moa e tunge mag kendo mar misango mar dhahabu manie nyim Nyasaye.  
\v 14 Eka dwolno nowacho ni malaika mar auchiel man-gi turumbete niya, “Gony malaike angʼwen motwe gibed thuolo gia e aora maduongʼ mar Yufrate.”  
\v 15 To nogony malaike angʼwen-go mane oseiki ni sa-no gi odiechiengno kod dweno gi higano, mondo gineg achiel kuom adek mar ji duto.  
\v 16 Kwan mar jolweny moidho farese ne oromo tara mia ariyo. Ne awinjo kar kwan-gi. 
\p  
\v 17 To farese gi joithgi mane aneno e fwenynano ne chalo kama: Joma noidhogi norwakore gi akor mag nyinyo makwar ka mach, kendo marambulu molil, kod ratongʼ gweno. Wi faresego ne chalo gi wi sibuoche, to mach gi yiro kod pilni mach ne wuok e dhogi.  
\v 18 Masiche adekgo mag mach, yiro kod pilni mag mach mane wuok e dho faresego nonego achiel kuom adek mar kwan ji duto.  
\v 19 Teko mane faresego nigo ne ni e dhogi kendo e iwgi nikech iwgi mane nigi wigi ne chalo gi thuonde man-gi wiye ma gikechogo ka gihinyogo ji. 
\p  
\v 20 To joma odongʼ mane masichego ok onego pod ne ok oweyo richo mar lamo gik mane giloso kendo gichweyo gi lwetgi; kendo ok giweyo lamo jochiende gi nyiseche manono molos gi dhahabu gi fedha kod mula gi kidi kod bao, ma gin gik ma ok nen bende ma ok winj wach, kendo ok wuothi.  
\v 21 Bende ne ok gilokore giweyo richo mar nego ji, kata timbe jwok kata terruok kata kuo mane gibedo ka gitimo. 
\c 10  
\s1 Malaika motingʼo kitabu matin 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne aneno malaika machielo maratego, kabiro lor aa e polo. Ne orwakore gi boche polo ka lihudu oumo wiye; wangʼe ne chalo gi wangʼ chiengʼ, kendo tiendene ne chalo gi sirni makakni ka mach.  
\v 2 Ne otingʼo kitabu matin moel e lwete. Nonyono nam gi tiende ma korachwich, to tiende ma koracham nonyonogo piny,  
\v 3 kendo nokok gi dwol maduongʼ machalo ka sibuor maruto. Bangʼ kosekok kamano to polo abiriyo nomor.  
\v 4 To kane polo abiriyogo osemor kamano, ne adwaro ndiko gima ne awinjo kagiwacho, eka nawinjo dwol moro moa e polo mowachona niya, “Kik indik gima polo abiriyogo osewacho to lingʼ-go mana ei chunyi.” 
\p  
\v 5 Eka malaika mane aneno konyono nam kod piny cha notingʼo bade korachwich kochomo polo.  
\v 6 Kendo nokwongʼore gi nying Jal mangima nyaka chiengʼ, Jal mane ochweyo polo gik moko duto manie iye, gi piny gi gik moko duto manie iye, kod nam gi gik moko duto manie iye kowacho niya, “Deko moro ok nochak obedie ngangʼ!”  
\v 7 To e kinde, ma malaika mar abiriyono nogo turumbetene, eka wach mopondo mar Nyasaye nochopi, mana kaka nonyiso jotichne ma jonabi. 
\p  
\v 8 Bangʼ mano dwol mane awinjo kawuoyo koa e polo cha ne ochako wuoyo koda kendo kawacho niya, “Dhiyo, ikaw kitabu moel manie lwet malaika ma onyono nam kod piny.” 
\p  
\v 9 Omiyo ne adhi ir malaikano, mi akwaye mondo omiya kitabu matin-no. To nowachona niya, “Kawe, mondo ichame. Obiro bedo makech e iyi, to e dhogi nobed mamit ka mor kich.”\f + \fr 10:9 \ft \xt Eze 3:3\f* 
\v 10 Eka nakawo kitabu matin-no manie lwet malaikano, mi achame, ne omit e dhoga ka mor kich to kane asechame nobedo makech e iya.  
\v 11 Bangʼe ne owachna niya, “Nyaka ichak ikor wach kuom ogendini mangʼeny, gi pinje mangʼeny kod joma wacho dhok mopogore opogore gi ruodhi mangʼeny.” 
\c 11  
\s1 Joneno ariyo 
\p  
\v 1 Eka nomiya rapim machalo gi luth mar pimo; kendo nowachona niya, “Aa malo idhiyo ipim hekalu mar Nyasaye kod kendo mar misango, kendo ikwan joma lemo kanyo!  
\v 2 To iwe laru ma oko manie nyim hekalu kik ipime, nikech osemiye joma ok jo-Yahudi, kendo gibiro nyone gi tiendegi ka giketho dala maler kuom dweche piero angʼwen gariyo.  
\v 3 To abiro miyo jonenona ariyo morwakore gi lep gugru teko, kendo ginihul wach Nyasaye kuom ndalo alufu achiel gi mia ariyo kod piero auchiel.”  
\v 4 Joneno ariyogo e yiende ariyo mag zeituni, kod rachungi teyni ariyo mochungʼ e nyim kom Ruodh piny.\f + \fr 11:4 \ft \xt Zek 4:3,11,14\f* 
\v 5 Ka ngʼato moro amora dwaro hinyogi, to mach wuok e dhogi matieko wasikgi. Mano e kaka ngʼato moro amora madwaro hinyogi notho.  
\v 6 Jogi nigi teko mar loro polo mondo koth kik chue e ndalo ma gihuloe wach. To bende gin gi teko mar loko pi obed remo kendo kelo tuoche yembe mopogore opogore e piny e kinde mora amora magidwaro. 
\p  
\v 7 To ka gisetieko hulo wechegi, ondiek mawuok e bur matut maonge gikone noked kodgi, mi nologi kendo negogi.  
\v 8 Ringregi noriere koriyo e yo mar dala maduongʼno, ma iluongo gi ngero ni Sodom kod Misri, dalano e kama nogurie Ruodhgi.  
\v 9 To ji moa e ogendini duto gi dhoudi, kod dhok duto ma ji wacho gi pinje duto, norang ringregi kuom ndalo adek gi nus, kendo ok giniyie mondo oyikgi.  
\v 10 Ji duto modak e piny nogo siboi kuom thogi, ka gimor kendo gimiyore chiwo, nikech jonabi ariyogo nosebedo kasando ji modak e piny. 
\p  
\v 11 To bangʼ ndalo adek gi nus much ngima mar Nyasaye nodonjo eigi, mine gichungʼ gi tiendegi, kendo luoro maduongʼ nomako joma ne onenogi.  
\v 12 Bangʼ mano negiwinjo dwol maduongʼ koa e polo kawachonegi niya, “Biuru malo ka!” Mine gidhi e polo malo ei bor polo moumogi, ka wasikgi nenogi. 
\p  
\v 13 E sa nogo piny noyiengni matek, mi achiel kuom apar mar bath dalano nomukore mogore piny, kendo ji alufu abiriyo notho e yiengni mar pinyno to joma nodongʼ nobwok malich, kendo negimiyo Nyasach Polo duongʼ! 
\p  
\v 14 Masira mar ariyo osekadho, neuru, masirano mar adek biro biro piyo. 
\s1 Turumbete mar abiriyo 
\p  
\v 15 Eka malaika mar abiriyo nogoyo turumbetene, to dwonde moko nokok matek ei polo, kagiwacho niya, 
\q1 “Pinyruodhi mar pinyni koro osedoko 
\q2 pinyruodhi mar Ruodhwa kendo mar Kristo, 
\q2 kendo enolochi nyaka chiengʼ.” 
\m  
\v 16 To jodongo piero ariyo gangʼwen mane obedo e kombegi mag duongʼ e nyim Nyasaye, nokulore piny auma kendo ne gidendo Nyasaye,  
\v 17 kagiwacho niya, 
\q1 “Wagoyoni erokamano, yaye Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego! 
\q2 Jal mantie, kendo Jal mane nitie, 
\q1 nikech isekawo teko mari maduongʼ, 
\q2 mi koro ichako locho. 
\q1  
\v 18 Nyiego nomako pinje mag ogendini, 
\q2 to koro mirimbi osechopo. 
\q1 Kinde osechopo mar ngʼado bura ni joma otho, 
\q2 kendo chiwo mich ni jotichni ma jonabi, 
\q1 gi jogi maler kod jogo moluoro nyingi, 
\q2 jomatindo gi jomadongo. 
\q1 Kendo tieko jogo maketho piny.” 
\p  
\v 19 Eka hekalu mar Nyasaye noyaw e polo, kendo Sandug Muma mar singruok nonenore ei hekalu; to mil polo marieny mager gi riadruok, koko kod mor polo gi yiengni mar piny nobetie kendo kodh pe nochwe mangʼeny. 
\c 12  
\s1 Dhako kod thuol malich 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ mano ranyisi malich nonenore ei polo. Ne en dhako morwakore gi wangʼ chiengʼ. Dwe ne ni e bwo tiende, to wiye nosidhie osimbo mar sulwe apar gariyo.  
\v 2 Ne en-gi ich, kendo noywak ka en girem nikech muoch ne kaye kodwaro nywol.  
\v 3 Eka ranyisi machielo bende nonenore ei polo: ne en thuol mangʼongo, makwar man-gi wiye abiriyo kod tunge apar gi osimbo abiriyo mosidhi e wiyene.  
\v 4 Iwe noywayo achiel kuom adek mar sulwe manie polo mi opudho kendo owitogi e piny. Thuol mangʼongono nochungʼ e nyim dhakono mane chiegni nywol, mondo ocham nyathine kosenywole.  
\v 5 Dhakono nonywolo nyathi ma wuowi, nyathi ma wuowi mabiro locho korito ogendini gi ludh nyinyo. To nyathineno noyudhi moter malo ir Nyasaye e kom duongʼne.  
\v 6 Dhakono noringo modhi e thim kuma ne Nyasaye oselosone mane ibiro ritee kuom ndalo alufu achiel gi mia ariyo kod piero auchiel. 
\p  
\v 7 Eka lweny nochakore e polo. Mikael gi malaike mage nokedo gi thuol malichno, to thuol mangʼongono gi malaike mage bende nokedo kodgi.  
\v 8 To thuol ne onge teko moromo, omiyo nologi kendo ne oriembgi e polo.  
\v 9 Eka thuol malichno nowit kidire mwalo e piny, thuol mangʼongo machon miluongo ni Jachien kata Satan, mawuondo piny ngima. Nowite modire e piny, kaachiel kod malaike mage bende. 
\p  
\v 10 Eka ne awinjo dwol maduongʼ moa e polo, kawacho niya, 
\q1 “Koro warruok gi teko 
\q2 kod pinyruodh Nyasachwa, 
\q2 gi loch mar Kristo osechopo. 
\q1 Nikech jahang jowetewa, 
\q2 mahangonegi e nyim Nyasachwa odiechiengʼ gi otieno, 
\q2 osewit modir e piny. 
\q1  
\v 11 Ne giloye 
\q2 gi remb Nyarombo, 
\q2 kendo gi Wach Nyasaye mane gihulo, 
\q1 bende ne ok gidew ngimagi ahinya 
\q2 mane nyalo miyo giluor tho. 
\q1  
\v 12 Emomiyo beduru mamor un polo, 
\q2 kod joma odak e iye! 
\q1 To mano kaka nobed malit ne piny gi nam, 
\q2 nikech Jachien oselor obiro iru! 
\q1 En gi mirima mager 
\q2 nikech ongʼeyo ni ndalo matin kende ema odongʼne.” 
\p  
\v 13 To kane thuol mangʼongono oneno ni osewite modire e piny, ne olawo dhako mane onywolo nyathi ma wuowi cha.  
\v 14 Dhakono nomi bwombe ariyo mag ongo maduongʼ mondo ohugo ochopgo kama nolosne e thim, kuma ne idhi ritee kimiye chiemo kuom higni adek gi nus kama thuol ok ne nyal chopoe ire.  
\v 15 Eka thuol nongʼogo pi moa e dhoge mamol ka aora mondo oyuogo dhakono gi oula mamol ka apaka.  
\v 16 To piny noyawo dhoge, momwonyo pi duto mane thuol mangʼongono nosengʼudho, mi nokonyo dhakono.  
\v 17 Eka thuol mangʼongono ne okecho gi dhakono, nodhi mondo oked gi nyithind dhakono modongʼ, morito chike Nyasaye kendo osiko motegno kahulo wach Yesu. 
\c 13  
\s1 Ondiegi mowuok e nam 
\p  
\v 1 Kendo ondiek malichno nochungʼ e dho nam. Eka naneno ondiek moro magalagala kawuok aa e nam. Ne en gi tunge apar kod wiye abiriyo. To nosidho osimbo apar e tungenego, kendo wich ka wich nondikie nying marach ma yanyo Nyasaye.  
\v 2 Ondiek mane anenono ne chalo gi kwach, to tiendene ne chalo tiende dubu, kendo dhoge ne chalo gi dho sibuor. To thuol mangʼongono nomiyo ondiegno tekone gi kome mar duongʼ gi lochne duto.  
\v 3 Achiel kuom wi ondiegno ne nenore ka gima ogo lero mar tho, to wiye mane ogo lerono nosechango. Ji duto manie piny nohum nono, kendo negiluwo bangʼ ondiegno.  
\v 4 To ji nolamo thuol mangʼongono nikech nosemiyo ondiek malichno tekone owuon kendo negilamo ondiek malichno ka gipenjo niya. “En ngʼa machal gi ondiek malich?” Ere ngʼato manyalo kedo kode? 
\p  
\v 5 Ondiek malichno nomi dhok mar wacho weche mag sungruok kod ayany, kendo ne oyiene bedo gi loch kuom dweche piero angʼwen gariyo.  
\v 6 Eka nochako wuoyo koyanyo Nyasaye kendo koketho nyinge kod kar dakne, kaachiel gi joma odak e polo.  
\v 7 Bende nomiye teko mondo oked gi jomaler mag Nyasaye kendo ologi, kendo nomiye loch kuom dhoudi duto, gi ogendini kod dhok duto miwacho gi pinje duto.  
\v 8 Ji duto modak e piny biro lamo ondiek malichno. Gin e joma nying-gi ok ondiki e kitabu mar ngima mar Nyarombo mane onegi chakre chwech piny. 
\p  
\v 9 Ngʼat man-gi it, mondo owinji! 
\q1  
\v 10 Ka ngʼato onego ter e twech 
\q2 to twech machalo kamano ema nyaka odhiye. 
\q1 Kendo ka ngʼato onego negi e lweny gi ligangla 
\q2 to liganglano ema nyaka negego. 
\m Ma e kinde ma jo-Nyasaye onego timie kinda kendo bed gi yie motegno. 
\s1 Ondiek malich moa e piny 
\p  
\v 11 Eka naneno ondiek malich machielo kawuok ei piny. Ne en gi tunge ariyo machalo gi mar nyarombo, to nowuoyo kaka thuol mangʼongo wuoyo.  
\v 12 Notiyo gi teko duto mar ondiek malich mokwongo ka en e nyim ondiegino. Eka nomiyo piny gi ji duto modak e iye olamo ondiek malich mokwongono, ma wiye ne nigi adhola malich mane ogo lero mar tho, to nosechango.  
\v 13 Notimo honni madongo ma kata mana mach nomiyo lor oa e polo, kabiro e piny ka ji duto neno.  
\v 14 To nowuondo ji modakie piny, nikech honni mane omiye teko mondo otim e nyim ondiek malich mokwongo. Ne ogolo chik mondo gilosi gima ket ma imiyogo duongʼ ondiek malich mokwongo mane ohiny gi ligangla to ok otho.  
\v 15 Nomiye teko mondo omi gima ket mar ondiek malich mokwongo muya, mondo owuo kendo one ni jogo duto mane otamore lamo gima ketno onegi.  
\v 16 Bende nochuno ji duto, jomatindo gi jomadongo, jo-mwandu kod jochan, wasumbini gi joma ni thuolo, mondo oket kido e lwetegi ma korachwich kata e lela wengegi,  
\v 17 mondo ngʼato angʼata kik ngʼiew kata loko gimoro amora, makmana ka en gi kidono ma en nying ondiek malichno kata namba mochungʼ kar nyingno. 
\p  
\v 18 To ngʼeyo tiend wachni dwaro rieko, Ngʼat man-gi rieko, mondo okwan namba mar ondiek, nikech nambano ochungʼ kar nying dhano. Nambano en mia auchiel gi piero auchiel gauchiel. 
\c 14  
\s1 Nyarombo gi ji alufu mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne angʼicho mi aneno Nyarombo kochungʼ ewi Got Sayun. To ne en kod ji alufu mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen (144,000) kendo nyinge owuon gi nying Wuon-gi nondiki e lela wengegi.  
\v 2 Eka ne awinjo dwol moro moa e polo ka wuo ka pi aora maringo matek kendo ka mor mar polo. Dwolno mane awinjo ne chalo gi jo-thumbe mag nyatiti magoyo nyatiti.  
\v 3 To ne giwero wer manyien ka gichungʼ e nyim kom duongʼ, kendo e nyim gik mangima angʼwen kod jodongogo. Bende ne onge ngʼato mane nyalo puonjore wero wendni makmana ogendini alufu mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen (144,000) mane gin joma nores koa e piny.  
\v 4 Jogi e joma ne ok odwanyore gi mon, to ne giritore maler. Giluwo bangʼ Nyarombo kamoro amora modhiye. Nongʼiewgi kigologi kuom ji migichalo kaka olembe mokwongo chiek michiwo ni Nyasaye kod Nyarombo.  
\v 5 Miriambo ne ok owuok e dhogi, bende gionge gi ketho moro amora. 
\s1 Malaike adek 
\p  
\v 6 Eka ne aneno malaika machielo ka huyo e kor polo. Ne en gi Injili mochwere mane olando ne ji duto modak e piny, nolando wachno ne pinje duto, gi dhoudi duto kod dhok duto gi ogendini duto.  
\v 7 Nokok gi dwol maduongʼ kowacho niya, “Luoruru Nyasaye kendo miyeuru duongʼ, nikech sa ma ongʼadoe bura osechopo! Lamuru Jal mane ochweyo polo gi piny kaachiel gi nam kod sokni mag pi.” 
\p  
\v 8 Eka malaika mar ariyo noluwe kawacho niya, “Yaye Babulon dala maduongʼ osepodho piny! Osepodho Piny! En e dhako cha mane omiyo ogendini duto omadho divai mar mer mar terruokne.” 
\p  
\v 9 Bangʼ mano, malaika mar adek nobiro bangʼ-gi kowacho gi dwol maduongʼ niya, “Ka ngʼato angʼata olamo ondiek malich kod gima ket kode, kendo ondikne kido e lela wangʼe kata e lwete,  
\v 10 ngʼatno, bende, nyaka nomadh divai mar mirimb Nyasaye, moseol mopongʼ giteko moo ei kikombe mar mirimbe. Noyud sand ei mach makakni e nyim malaika maler, kendo e nyim Nyarombo.  
\v 11 To iro mar mach mar sandgino dhi malo nyaka chiengʼ. Jogo malamo ondiek malich kod gima ket kode, kata jogo mondik negi kido mar nyinge, ok noyud yweyo odiechiengʼ kata otieno.”  
\v 12 Ngʼeyo tiend wachni dwaro kinda kod dhil mar joma rito chike mag Nyasaye, kendo osiko koyie kuom Yesu. 
\p  
\v 13 Eka nawinjo dwol moa e polo kawacho niya, “Ndik ni: Chakre kawuononi, jogo gin joma ogwedhi matho kogeno kuom Ruoth!” 
\p Roho bende wacho ni, “Ee, gin johawi adier, nikech giniywe kuom tichgi matek, nimar timbegi noluwgi.” 
\s1 Keyo mar piny 
\p  
\v 14 To ne angʼicho, mi naneno bor polo marachar e nyima, to ewi bor polono ne nitie ngʼama obetie “machalo gi wuod dhano.”\f + \fr 14:14 \ft \xt Dan 7:13\f* Nosidho osimbo mar dhahabu e wiye, kendo ne otingʼo pala mabith mar keyo e lwete.  
\v 15 Eka malaika machielo nowuok oa e hekalu kaluongo jal mobedo e bor polono gi dwol maduongʼ niya, “Kaw pandi mar keyo mondo ike, nikech sa mar keyo osechopo, nimar cham manie piny, osechiek.”  
\v 16 Omiyo jal mane obet e bor polo notiyo gi pande mar keyo e piny, mi nokayo piny ka cham. 
\p  
\v 17 To malaika machielo nowuok oa e hekalu manie polo, en bende ne en gi pala mabith mar keyo.  
\v 18 Eka malaika moro machielo, mane nigi teko kuom mach, noa e kar kendo mar misango kendo noluongo gi dwol maduongʼ jalno mane nigi pala mabith mar keyo kowachone niya, “Kaw pandi mabithno mar keyo mondo ikago olemb mzabibu mag piny, nikech olembene ochiek ahinya!”  
\v 19 Omiyo malaikano notiyo gi pande mar keyo e piny, ne okayo olembe mzabibu kendo noketogi kar biyo mzabibu maduongʼ mar mirimb Nyasaye.  
\v 20 Olembego ne obi kinyonogi gi tielo e kar bichono e pap oko mar dala, to remo nochwer kamol kawuok kar bichono, mochopo mabor moromo kilomita mia adek koa e dala, to tut remono ne nyalo romo fut abich. 
\c 15  
\s1 Malaike abiriyo gi masiche abiriyo 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne aneno ranyisi machielo malich ahinya ei polo: Ne aneno Malaike abiriyo, motingʼo masiche abiriyo, mago ne masiche mogik nikech ka girumo to mirimb Nyasaye chopo kare.  
\v 2 Ne aneno gima chalo gi nam mar kio mar rangʼi moruwore gi mach to e bathe kanyo ne aneno joma oseloyo ondiek malichno kod kido machalo kode to gi namba mar nyinge kochungʼ. Negitingʼo nyatiti mane omigi gi Nyasaye,  
\v 3 ka giwero wend Musa jatich Nyasaye gi wend Nyarombo kama: 
\q1 “Yaye Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego, 
\q2 mano kaka tijeni dongo kendo lich. 
\q1 Yaye Ruodh Nyasaye ogendini, 
\q2 yoreni nikare kendo gin adiera. 
\q1  
\v 4 En ngʼa, ma ok nyal luori aa Ruoth, 
\q2 ma ok nyal miyo nyingi duongʼ? 
\q1 Nikech in kendi ema iler, 
\q1 ogendini duto nobi 
\q2 e nyimi mondo olami, 
\q1 nimar timbeni makare osefwenyore ratiro.” 
\p  
\v 5 Eka ne angʼiyo mi aneno ka hekalu mar Hemb Rapar oyawore e polo.  
\v 6 Malaike abiriyo motingʼo masiche abiriyo nowuok e hekalu. Ne girwakore gi lewni maler mapakni kendo manyilni to negitweyo okanda mar dhahabu e korgi.  
\v 7 Achiel kuom gik mangima angʼwen ka ne omiyo malaike abiriyogo tewni abiriyo mag dhahabu mopongʼ gi mirimb Nyasaye mosiko nyaka chiengʼ.  
\v 8 Hekalu ne iye opongʼ gi iro moa e duongʼ maler mar Nyasaye kod tekone. To onge ngʼama ne nyalo donjo ei hekalu kapok masiche abiriyo mag malaike abiriyogo orumo. 
\c 16  
\s1 Tewni abiriyo mag mirimb Nyasaye 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne awinjo dwol maduongʼ kakok koa ei hekalu kawuoyo gi malaike abiriyogo kawachonegi niya, “Koro dhiuru, mondo upuk tewni abiriyo mopongʼ gi mirimb Nyasaye e piny.” 
\p  
\v 2 Malaika mokwongo nodhi mopuko tape e piny, mi adhonde malich mangʼwe marach ne omako ji duto mane nigi kido mar ondiek malich kendo mane lamo gima ket kode. 
\p  
\v 3 Eka Malaika mar ariyo noolo tape e nam mi pi nam nolokore remo machalo gi remb ngʼat motho, kendo gik mangima duto modak e nembego ne otho. 
\p  
\v 4 Kamano bende Malaika mar adek noolo tape e aore gi sokni mag pi kendo pigegi ne olokore remo.  
\v 5 Bangʼe ne awinjo malaika mochungʼne pige kawacho niya, 
\q1 “In kare kuom kelo kumgi, 
\q2 yaye Nyasaye mantie kendo mane nitie bende in e Jal Maler, 
\q2 nikech isengʼado bura kare; 
\q1  
\v 6 nimar jogi ne osechwero remb jogi maler, 
\q2 gi jonabi mane onegi, 
\q1 to koro isemiyo gimadho remo mana 
\q2 kaka owinjore kodgi.” 
\m  
\v 7 Eka ne awinjo dwol kawuok e kendo mar misango kawacho niya, 
\q1 “En adieri Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego 
\q2 ni kumni nikare kendo gin adieri.” 
\p  
\v 8 Bangʼ mano Malaika mar angʼwen noolo tape e wangʼ chiengʼ, mi wangʼ chiengʼ nomi teko mar wangʼo ji ka mach mager.  
\v 9 Liet mager mar chiengʼ nowangʼogi to negidhi nyime mana giyanyo nying Nyasaye man-gi teko mar gengʼo masichego, kendo negitamore hulo richogi mondo gimiye duongʼ. 
\p  
\v 10 Eka malaika mar abich noolo tape ewi kom duongʼ mar ondiek malichno, to pinyruodhe nolokore mudho. Ji nokayo lewgi nikech rem malit mane gin-go  
\v 11 kendo ne giyanyo Nyasach polo nikech rem mane gin-go gi adhondegi; to kata kamano negitamore lokore weyo richo mane gisetimo. 
\p  
\v 12 Bangʼe malaika mar auchiel noolo tape e aora maduongʼ mar Yufrate, mi pige noduono mondo yo olosre ni ruodhi mane biro koa yo wuok chiengʼ.  
\v 13 Eka naneno jochiende adek machalo ogwende, ka wuok e dho thuol mangʼongono kendo e dho ondiek malich kendo e dho janabi mar miriambo.  
\v 14 Gin chunje mag jochiende matimo timbe honni kendo gidhi ir ruodhi duto mag piny ngima mondo gichokgi ni lweny ma nobedie chiengʼ maduongʼ mar Nyasaye Maratego. 
\b  
\mi  
\v 15 \wj “Neuru! Abiro apoya mana kaka jakuo! Ngʼatno en ngʼat mogwedhi ma nonwangʼ kaneno kendo ma orwako lepe mondo wiye kik kuodi ka oyude duk.”\wj* 
\b  
\m  
\v 16 Bangʼ mano chunjego nochoko ruodhigo kanyakla kama iluongo gi dho jo-Hibrania ni Armagedon. 
\p  
\v 17 Kendo malaika mar abiriyo bende noolo tape e yamo; eka dwol maduongʼ nowuok koa ei hekalu e nyim kom maduongʼ mar loch kawacho niya, “Osetimore!”  
\v 18 Bangʼ mano, ne nitie mil polo makakni, koriadore kod mor polo gi yiengni malich mar piny. Piny noyiengni matek mapok oyiengni kamano nyaka aa chwech dhano. Adiera chutho ne en yiengni mar piny, marachie moloyo.  
\v 19 Dala maduongʼ nobarore mopogore nyadidek kendo mier madongo mag pinje ogendini nomukore mogore piny. Nyasaye noparo Babulon dala maduongʼ, mine omiye kikombe mopongʼ gi divai mar mirimbe mager.  
\v 20 Chula ka chula nolal nono kendo gode duto bende nolal kamano.  
\v 21 Pe madongo dongo ma pek moro ka moro dirom kilo piero abich, noa e polo mogoyo ji. To ne giyanyo Nyasaye nikech masirano mar pe, nimar ne en masira marach moloyo! 
\c 17  
\s1 Dhako ma jachode 
\p  
\v 1 Eka achiel kuom malaike abiriyo mane nigi tewni abiriyo nobiro ira, mowachona niya; “Bi mondo anyisi kum mar jachode maduongʼ mobet ewi pige mangʼeny.  
\v 2 En ema ruodhi mag piny noterore kode, kendo ji duto modak e piny bende osemadho divai mar terruokne mi omer.” 
\p  
\v 3 Bangʼe Roho noyudha kendo malaika nokawa motera e thim. Mana gikanyono naneno dhako moro koidho ondiek malich makwar, ma dende duto nochadhore gi nyinge mag ayany, kendo ne en gi wiye abiriyo kod tunge apar.  
\v 4 Dhakono norwakore gi lewni maralik gi makwar, kendo nolichore gi dhahabu kod kite mabeyo ma nengogi tek gi lulu. To notingʼo kikombe mar dhahabu e lwete, mopongʼ gi gik makwero kod timbe mochido mag terruokne.  
\v 5 Kendo nying mane ondik e lela wangʼe ne en gima iwuoro: 
\pc Babulon maduongʼ 
\pc Min jochode duto 
\pc kendo min gik makwero mag piny. 
\m  
\v 6 Bende ne aneno dhakono komer gi remb jomaler mag Nyasaye, remb jogo mane ohulo ni Yesu e Ruoth. 
\p Kane anene ne awuoro ahinya.  
\v 7 Eka malaika cha nopenja niya, “Angʼo miwuoro kamano? Abiro nyisi tiend wach mopondo mar dhakono kod mar ondiek malich moidho gi wiye abiriyo kod tunge apar.  
\v 8 Ondiek malich mane inenono, yande nitie, to tinde oonge kendo obiro wuok oa e bur matut maonge gikone ka odhiyo e kar kethruokne. Ji duto modak e piny, ma nyingegi ok ondiki e kitap ngima nyaka aa chakruok mar piny nowuor ka gineno ondiek malichno, nikech yande entie to tinde oonge, to nochak oduogi kendo. 
\p  
\v 9 “Ngʼeyo tiend wachni dwaro paro matut man-gi rieko. Wiye abiriyogo gin gode abiriyo ma dhakono obetie.  
\v 10 To bende gin ruodhi abiriyo. Ma abich kuomgi osepodho, to achiel pod nitie, to machielo pod ok obiro; to ka obiro to nobedi kuom thuolo matin.  
\v 11 Ondiek malichno ma yande nitie, to tinde onge, en ruoth mar aboro. Bende en achiel kuom ruodhi abiriyogo, kendo odhiyo e kar kethruokne. 
\p  
\v 12 “Tunge apargo mane ineno, gin ruodhi apar mapok oyudo pinyruoth to ibiro miyogi teko mar locho kuom sa achiel kende, kaka ruodhi kaachiel gi ondiek malichno.  
\v 13 Gin duto gin gi paro achiel kendo ginichiw tekogi kod lochgi ni ondiek malichno.  
\v 14 Giniked gi Nyarombo, to Nyarombo nologi nikech en e Jaloch mar joloch, kendo Ruoth mar ruodhi, to jogo mane obed kode, gin joge moluongi, joma oyier gi jogo maluwe gadiera.” 
\p  
\v 15 Eka malaikano nowachona niya, “Pigego mane ineno ma dhako ma jachode obedoe, gin ji gi ogendini mangʼeny kod dhout pinje gi joma wacho dhok mopogore opogore.  
\v 16 To ondiek malichno gi tunge apargo mane ineno biro bedo mager kod dhakono ma jachode. Ginihinye kagitieke kendo weye duk; ginicham ringre, kendo giniwangʼe duto gi mach.  
\v 17 Nimar Nyasaye oseketo e chunygi mondo gitim gima odwaro ka gimiyo ondiek lochgi mondo olochi, nyaka wach Nyasaye chopi.  
\v 18 Dhakono mane ineno en e dala maduongʼ man-gi loch kuom ruodhi mag piny.” 
\c 18  
\s1 Babulon opodho 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ wechego ne aneno malaika machielo kalor piny aa e polo. Ne en gi teko maduongʼ, kendo lerne ne menyo piny.  
\v 2 Nokok gi dwol maduongʼ kowacho niya, 
\q1 “Yaye Babulon dala maduongʼ osepodho piny! Osepodho piny! 
\q2 Osedoko kar dak mar jochiende, 
\q1 kendo odoko gunda ma chuny duto mochido odakie, 
\q2 kaachiel gi winy duto ma ok ler kendo makwero. 
\q1  
\v 3 Mano osetimore nikech ogendini e pinje duto 
\q2 osemadho divai makech mar terruokne. 
\q1 Ruodhi mag piny oseterore kode, 
\q2 kendo jo-ohala mag piny bende osedoko jo-mwandu 
\q2 nikech ohala mangimane mamalo osekelonegi.” 
\p  
\v 4 Eka nawinjo dwol moro machielo moa e polo kawacho niya, 
\q1 “ ‘Un joga, wuoguru ua kuome,’\f + \fr 18:4 \ft \xt Jer 51:45\f* 
\q2 mondo kik ubed achiel kode e richone, 
\q2 mondo kik unwangʼ masichene, 
\q1  
\v 5 nikech richone osebiwore mochopo e polo malo, 
\q2 kendo Nyasaye koro oseparo timbene mamonogo. 
\q1  
\v 6 Timneuru kaka osetimono! 
\q2 Medneuru nyadiriyo kuom gik ma osetimo! 
\q2 Losneuru mathne mane omiyo ji e kikombene nyadiriyo. 
\q1  
\v 7 Miyeuru sand kod ywagruok mangʼeny 
\q2 marom gi duongʼ kod dhialruok mar ngima 
\q2 moyombore mane odakie kendo mane omiyore owuon. 
\q1 Ne osungore kowacho e chunye niya, 
\q2 ‘Abedo kaka ruoth ma dhako, 
\q1 ok an dhako ma chwore otho 
\q2 kendo ok ane gima dimi aywag ngangʼ.’\f + \fr 18:7 \ft \xt Isa 47:7,8\f* 
\q1  
\v 8 Emomiyo masichene chiengʼ moro achiel noloye; 
\q2 masichego gin tho gi ywagruok kod kech. 
\q1 Nowangʼe gi mach, 
\q2 nikech Ruoth Nyasaye mangʼadone bura, 
\q2 nigi teko maduongʼ moloyo! 
\p  
\v 9 “To ruodhi mag piny mane oterore kode, kendo bedo kode e ngima moyombore noywage kendo sedo kod nyinge ka gineno yiro madum ka owangʼ.  
\v 10 Ginichungʼ mabor ka giluoro sandne kendo ka giywak niya, 
\q1 “ ‘To mano kaka lit! To mano kaka lit! Yaye dala maduongʼ. 
\q2 Yaye Babulon, dala maduongʼ man-gi teko! 
\q1 Kethruokni osechoponi kuom sa achiel kende!’ ” 
\p  
\v 11 Johala mag piny noywage ka gidengo, nikech onge ngʼat manochak ongʼiew mwandugi kendo.  
\v 12 Mwandugigo gin: dhahabu gi fedha kod kite mabeyo ma nengogi tek gi lulu kod lewni mabeyo, gi lewni maralik, lewni mayom kod lewni makwar gi yien duto madungʼ tik mangʼwe ngʼar, gi gik moko duto molos gi lak liech, gi yien ma nengogi tek kod molos gi nyinyo, kod mula kendo molos gi kite mabeyo,  
\v 13 kod gik moko kaka obala ndago gi gik mangʼwe ngʼar; kaka ubani gi mor pwodhruok madungʼ tik mangʼwe ngʼar kod uvumba gi divai kod mo mzabibu gi mogo mayom gi ngano kod dhok gi rombe gi farese gi geche lweny kod ringruok gi chunje ji bende. 
\p  
\v 14 “Giniwach niya, ‘Olembe ma yande igombo oserumoni. Mwandugi duto kod gik mabeyo malombo wangʼ oselal chutho, ok nibed kodgi kendo ngangʼ.’  
\v 15 Jo-ohala mane oloko gigegi kendo obedo momewo nikech gigegego nochungʼ mabor, ka giluor nikech sandruokne. Giniywagi kagidengo,  
\v 16 kendo goyo nduru kagiwacho niya: 
\q1 “ ‘Mano kaka lit! Mano kaka lit, yaye dala maduongʼ, 
\q2 morwakore gi lewni mayom kod lewni marep-rep gi makwar, 
\q2 mapakni gi dhahabu gi kite mabeyo ma nengogi tek kod lulu! 
\q1  
\v 17 Mano kaka mwandu mathoth kama osekethi motieki kuom sa achiel kende!’ 
\p “Jotend yiedhi duto, gi jowuoth duto mawuotho gi yiedhi kod jokwangʼ yiedhi gi jogo duto maloko ohala e nam, ginichungʼ gichien.  
\v 18 Ka gineno iro mar Babulon kadum kowangʼ, negiwacho ni, ‘Bende ne nitie dala moro machalo gi dala maduongʼni?’  
\v 19 Ginibuk wigi gi buru ka gigoyo nduru niya, 
\q1 “ ‘Mano kaka lit! Mano kaka lit, yaye dala maduongʼ, 
\q2 kama ji duto mane nigi yiedhi e nam, 
\q2 nobedo joma omewo nikech mwandune. 
\q1 Mano kaka osekethe kendo otieke chutho mana kuom sa achiel kende!’ 
\b  
\q1  
\v 20 “Yaye polo bed mamor kuom kethne. 
\q2 Un jomaler mag Nyasaye gi joote kod jonabi, beduru mamor! 
\q1 Nyasaye osengʼadone bura kendo kume nikech timbe mane otimonu.” 
\p  
\v 21 Eka malaika maratego nokawo kidi machalo gi pongʼ rego maduongʼ, notingʼe kendo nobole e nam, kowacho niya, 
\q1 “Kamano 
\q2 e kaka Babulon dala maduongʼ nobol piny, 
\q2 mi ok nonene ngangʼ. 
\q1  
\v 22 Wende jogo thum nyatiti gi jower, 
\q2 kod jogo asili gi jogo tungʼ, 
\q2 ok nowinj kuomi ngangʼ. 
\q1 Kata ja-ohala moro amora 
\q2 ok noyud kuomi ngangʼ, 
\q1 bende pongʼ marego 
\q2 ok nowinj kuomi ngangʼ. 
\q1  
\v 23 Ler mar taya 
\q2 ok norieny kendo e iyi chutho. 
\q1 Dwond wuon kisera gi dwond miaha bende 
\q2 ok nochak owinj e iyi ngangʼ. 
\q1 Jolok ohala magi ne gin ji madongo e piny. 
\q2 To pinje duto nobaro mokethore nikech wuondni kod timbeni mayore mag jwok. 
\q1  
\v 24 Ne oyud kuome remb jonabi gi remb jomaler, 
\q2 kod remb ji duto mane osenegi e piny.” 
\c 19  
\s1 Mor maduongʼ manie polo! 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼ mano, nawinjo gima chalo gi koko maduongʼ mar oganda ei polo kawacho niya, 
\q1 “Haleluya! 
\q1 Warruok gi duongʼ kod teko odog ne Nyasachwa, 
\q2  
\v 2 nikech buchene gin adiera kendo kare. 
\q1 Osengʼado bura ni jachode maduongʼ 
\q2 mane oketho piny gi terruokne. 
\q1 Adier Nyasaye osekume nikech nonego jotich Nyasaye.” 
\p  
\v 3 Eka negigoyo koko kendo niya, 
\q1 “Haleluya! 
\q1 Iro moa kuome kowangʼ nodum mochwere manyaka chiengʼ.” 
\p  
\v 4 To jodongo piero ariyo gangʼwen gi gik mangima angʼwen-go, nopodho piny auma kendo gidendo Nyasaye mane obedo e kom duongʼ mar loch. Ne giywak niya, 
\q1 “Amin! Haleluya!” 
\p  
\v 5 Eka dwol noa e kom duongʼ mar loch, kawacho niya, 
\q1 “Pakuru Nyasachwa, 
\q2 un jotichne duto, 
\q1 un joge moluore, 
\q2 jomatindo kod jomadongo!” 
\p  
\v 6 Bangʼe ne awinjo gima chalo gi koko mar oganda mangʼeny machalo gi koko mar pige maringo matek, bende machalo gi polo mamor matek, kawacho niya, 
\q1 “Ruoth omi duongʼ! Haleluya! 
\q2 Nimar Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego olosecho. 
\q1  
\v 7 Wabeduru moil kendo mamor ahinya 
\q2 kendo wamiyeuru duongʼ! 
\q1 Nikech kinde kisera mar Nyarombo osechopo, 
\q2 kendo chiege oseikne. 
\q1  
\v 8 Osemiye law mayom, mapichni kendo maler, 
\q2 mondo orwaki.” 
\m Law maberno ochungʼ kar timbe makare mag jomaler. 
\b  
\p  
\v 9 Eka malaikano nowachona niya, “Ndik kama: Jogo gin joma ogwedhi moluongi e kisera mar Nyarombo!” Bangʼe nomedo wacho niya, “Magi gin weche ma adier mag Nyasaye.” 
\p  
\v 10 Bangʼe napodho piny e tiende mondo alame. To nowachona niya, “Ngangʼ! Kik itim kamano! An bende an mana jatich wadu matiyo kodi kaachiel gi oweteni mahulo wach kuom Yesu gichir. Nyasaye kende ema owinjore ilam! Wach adieri man kuom Yesu ema miyo jonabi Roho mar koro wach mar Yesu.” 
\s1 Ngʼat moidho faras marachar 
\p  
\v 11 Eka naneno polo koyawore kendo naneno faras marachar kochungo e nyima ma jaithne iluongo ni Ja-ratiro, kendo Ja-adiera. Nikech ongʼado buchene e yo makare kendo okedo lwenjene gi ratiro.  
\v 12 Wengene liel ka mach makakni, to osimbo mangʼeny ni e wiye. En gi nying mondik kuome, maonge ngʼama ongʼeyo, makmana en owuon.  
\v 13 Kendo orwakore gi kandho molingʼ e remo, to nyinge en Wach Nyasaye.  
\v 14 Jolweny mag polo ne luwo bangʼe, ka giidho farese marochere kendo ka girwakore gi lewni mayom marochere kendo maler.  
\v 15 To ligangla mabith wuok e dhoge ma ochwowogo ogendini manie pinje. Obiro locho koritogi gi ludh nyinyo.\f + \fr 19:15 \ft \xt Zab 2:9\f* To enonyon-gi ka jabicho mar divai ka oolo mirimb Nyasaye Maratego kuomgi.  
\v 16 En gi nying moro mondik e kandhone kendo e bamne ni: 
\pc Jaloch mar joloch kendo Ruoth mar ruodhi. 
\p  
\v 17 To bangʼe ne aneno malaika moro kochungʼe wangʼ chiengʼ, nogoyo koko gi dwol maduongʼ ne winy duto mane huyo e kor polo niya, “Biuru, uchokru kaachiel e kar sawo maduongʼ mar Nyasaye,  
\v 18 mondo ucham ring ruodhi, gi ring jotend lweny kod ring joma rateke, gi ring farese kod joithgi kaachiel gi ring ji duto, joma ni thuolo gi wasumbini, jomatindo gi jomadongo.” 
\p  
\v 19 Eka naneno ondiek malichno gi ruodhi mag piny kod ogendinigi mag lweny kochokore kaachiel mondo giked gi Jal moidho faras kod ogandane mar lweny.  
\v 20 To ne omak ondiek malichno kaachiel gi janabi mar miriambo, mane osetimo timbe honni e nyinge. Honnigo ema ne osewuondogo joma ne oketnegi kido mar ondiek malichno kendo negilamo gima ket kode. Ondiek malichno gi Janabi mar miriambo ne owiti kangima e ataro mar mach maliel mager.  
\v 21 To jogegi mane odongʼ noneg gi ligangla mane owuok e dho jaidh faras, kendo winy duto nokidho ringregi. 
\c 20  
\s1 Higni alufu achiel 
\p  
\v 1 Eka naneno malaika kalor koa e polo, kotingʼo rayaw mar bur matut maonge gikone kod nyororo maduongʼ e lwete.  
\v 2 Ne omako thuol mangʼongono tiende ni thuol machon, ma en Jachien kata Satan matek, kendo notweye kuom higni alufu achiel.  
\v 3 Ne owite e Bur Matut Maonge gikone, kendo nolorone modinone e iye, mondo kik ochak owuond ogendini mag pinje ngangʼ nyaka higni alufu achielgo rum. To bangʼe nogonye mondo obed thuolo kuom kinde matin. 
\p  
\v 4 Bangʼ mano, ne aneno kombe mag loch, ma joma ne obetie nosemi teko mar ngʼado bura. Bende ne aneno chuny joma ne osengʼad wiyegi nikech wach yie margi motegno mane gihulo kuom Yesu kendo wach Nyasaye mane gilando. Jogi ne ok olamo ondiek malichno kata gima ket kode kendo kido mare ne ok oket e lela wengegi kata lwetegi. Negidoko mangima kendo negilocho gi Kristo kuom higni alufu achiel.  
\v 5 Ma e chier mokwongo. To joma otho mane odongʼ mane ok ochier e chierni, ne ok odoko mangima nyaka higni alufu achielgo norumo.  
\v 6 Joma ochier e chier mokwongoni gin joma ogwedhi kendo mopwodhi. Tho mar ariyo onge gi teko kuomgi, to ginibed jodolo mag Nyasaye kod mag Kristo kendo giniloch kode kuom higni alufu achiel. 
\s1 Satan olo 
\p  
\v 7 To bangʼ ka higni alufu achiel oserumo, Satan nogony mobed thuolo koa e bur mane otweye,  
\v 8 kendo nowuog oko mondo owuond ogendini duto mag tunge angʼwen mag piny, ma gin Gog gi Magog, kendo nochokgi kaachiel mondo gidhi e lweny. To kar kwan-gi romre gi kwoyo manie dho nam.  
\v 9 Ne giwuotho mi gikwako piny duto, kendo negilworo kambi mar jo-Nyasaye, dala maduongʼ ma Nyasaye ohero. To mach ne oa e polo mobiro e piny kendo nowangʼogi motiekogi.  
\v 10 To Jachien, mane owuondogi ne owit e ataro mar mach maliel mager, kama ondiek malichno kod janabi mar miriambo nowitie. Kanyo gini sandre odiechiengʼ gi otieno nyaka chiengʼ. 
\s1 Bura mogik 
\p  
\v 11 Eka naneno kom mar loch maduongʼ marachar kaachiel gi jal manobedo e komno. Piny gi polo noringo oa e nyime mi olal nono ma ok nonegi kendo.  
\v 12 Bende ne aneno joma otho, jomadongo gi jomatindo, negichungʼ e nyim kom maduongʼ mar loch, kendo kitepe noel. Kitabu moro noel, ma en kitap ngima. Joma otho nongʼadnigi bura kaluwore kod gik mane gisetimo kaka ondiki e kitepego.  
\v 13 Nam nogolo joma otho manie iye, to Tho gi Piny Joma otho nogolo joma otho manie igi, kendo ngʼato ka ngʼato nongʼadne bura koluwore kod gik mane osetimo.  
\v 14 Eka tho gi Piny Joma otho nowiti e ataro mar mach. Ataro mar mach en e tho mar ariyo.  
\v 15 Ngʼato angʼata ma nyinge ne ok onwangʼ kondiki e kitap ngima, nowit e ataro mar mach. 
\c 21  
\s1 Jerusalem manyien gi piny manyien 
\p  
\v 1 Eka ne aneno polo manyien gi piny manyien. Polo mokwongo gi piny mokwongo noselal, to nam bende noselal kamano.  
\v 2 Bangʼe naneno Dala Maduongʼ Maler, ma en Jerusalem manyien kalor piny oa e polo ir Nyasaye, ka oikore ka miaha morwakore maber ni chwore.  
\v 3 To ne awinjo dwol maduongʼ moa e kom duongʼ mar loch mawacho niya, “Koro Nyasaye osebiro dak gi ji kendo enodag kodgi, ginibed joge, to Nyasaye owuon enobed kodgi kendo nobed Nyasachgi.  
\v 4 Enoywe pi wengegi duto. Tho kata ywak gi nduru kod rem ok nochak obedie kendo ngangʼ, nikech gik machon oserumo.” 
\p  
\v 5 Jal manobedo e kom duongʼ mar loch nowacho niya, “Neuru! Aloso gik moko duto bedo manyien!” Eka nowachona kendo niya, “Ndik ma, nikech wechegi gin migeno kendo gin adiera.” 
\p  
\v 6 Bangʼ mano nowachona niya, “Gik moko osetimore. An e Alfa gi Omega, Chakruok gi Giko. Ngʼat ma riyo oloyo anami omodh pi soko mar ngima nono ma ok ochulo gimoro.  
\v 7 Ngʼat molocho noyud gigi duto kaka girkeni, kendo anabed Nyasache, to enobed wuoda.  
\v 8 To joma luor, gi joma ok oyie kod jo-koko gi jonek kod joma terore, gi jojuogi gi joma lamo nyiseche manono kod jo-miriambo duto, kargi nobed mana ataro mar mach maliel mager, ma en tho mar ariyo!” 
\p  
\v 9 Eka achiel kuom malaike abiriyogo mane nigi tewni abiriyo motingʼo masiche abiriyo mogik nobiro ira mowachona niya, “Bi, mondo anyisi miaha ma en chi Nyarombo.”  
\v 10 Roho nopongʼa kendo malaikano notingʼa motera malo ewi got mabor, mi nonyisa Jerusalem, ma en Dala Maduongʼ Maler, kalor piny aa e polo ir Nyasaye.  
\v 11 Ne orieny gi ler mar duongʼ Nyasaye, to lerne ne rieny ka kidi ma nengone tek, kaka jaspa maler ahinya.  
\v 12 Ne en gi ohinga maduongʼ kendo mabor man-gi dhorangeye apar gariyo kendo man-gi malaike apar gariyo e dhorangeyego. Bende e dhorangeyego nondikie nying ogendini apar gariyo mag Israel.  
\v 13 Dhorangeye adek ne ni yo wuok chiengʼ, to adek yo nyandwat, kendo adek yo milambo bende adek mamoko yo podho chiengʼ.  
\v 14 To ohinga mar dalano ne nigi mise apar gariyo, mane ondikie nying joote apar gariyo mag Nyarombo. 
\p  
\v 15 Malaikano mane owuoyo koda, ne nigi luth mar rapim molos gi dhahabu mipimogo dalano, gi dhorangeyene kod ohingane.  
\v 16 Dalano noger ma bethene angʼwen romre, ka borne ne rom gi lachne. Nopimo dala gi luth kendo noyudo ni borne gi lachne kod borne modhi malo ne romo kilomita alufu ariyo gi mia ariyo (2,200) maromre.  
\v 17 Bende ne opimo ohingane, mi oyudo ni pek mar kore oromo bede mia achiel gi piero angʼwen gangʼwen, kipimo gi bat mar dhano, ma en rapim mane malaika otiyogo.  
\v 18 Ohingano noger gi jaspa, to dalano noger gi dhahabu lilo marieny ka kio maler.  
\v 19 Mise mar ohinga mar dala nokedi gi kite mabeyo duto ma nengogi tek. Mise mokwongo nolos gi jaspa, to mar ariyo ne safir, eka mar adek ne kalkedo kendo mar angʼwen ne emerald,  
\v 20 to mar abich ne sardonikso, mar auchiel ne sardius, eka mar abiriyo ne krusolith, to mar aboro ne berul, mar ochiko ne topaz, to mar apar ne kruskopraso, kendo mar apar gachiel ne jasinth, to mar apar gariyo ne amethusto.  
\v 21 Dhorangeye apar gariyogo ne gin kite mag lulu ma nengogi tek, kendo dhorangach ka dhorangach nolos gi lulu achiel achiel moriwore. Yor dalano ne dhahabu lilo marieny maler ka kio. 
\p  
\v 22 To ne ok aneno hekalu ei dalano, nikech Ruoth Nyasaye Maratego kod Nyarombo ema obedo hekalu mare.  
\v 23 Dalano ok dwar chiengʼ kata dwe mondo orienyne, nikech duongʼ Nyasaye ema miye ler, kendo Nyarombo e tache.  
\v 24 Ogendini nowuothi e lerne, kendo ruodhi mag pinje nokel duongʼ-gi e iye.  
\v 25 Dhorangeyene ok nolor odiechiengʼ moro amora, to otieno bende ok nobedie ngangʼ.  
\v 26 Duongʼ gi mwandu mag ogendini mag pinje nokel e iye.  
\v 27 To gimoro amora ma ok ler, kata ngʼato matimo gik makwero, kata mariambo, ok nodonjie, makmana jogo ma nying-gi ondiki e kitap Nyarombo mar ngima kende. 
\c 22  
\s1 Aora mar ngima 
\p  
\v 1 Bangʼe eka malaika nonyisa aora mar pi mar ngima, marieny maler ahinya, kendo mamol kawuok e kom duongʼ mar loch mar Nyasaye gi mar Nyarombo,  
\v 2 ne omol e dier yo maduongʼ mar dalano. To bath aora koni gi koni ne nitie yath mar ngima manyago olembe kido apar gariyo kendo ne onyago olembegego dwe ka dwe, bende ite yadhno ema ithiedhogo ogendini mag pinje.  
\v 3 Gik ma Nyasaye okwedo ok nochak obedie. Kom duongʼ mar loch Nyasaye gi mar Nyarombo ema nobedie ei dalano, to jotichne notine.  
\v 4 Gininene wangʼ gi wangʼ kendo nyinge nobed e lela wangʼ-gi.  
\v 5 Otieno ok nobedie kendo ngangʼ bende ok ginidwar ler mar taya kata ler mar chiengʼ, nikech Ruoth Nyasaye ema nomigi ler. To ginibed gi loch nyaka chiengʼ. 
\p  
\v 6 Eka malaikano nowachona niya, “Wechegi gin weche mogen kendo ma adiera. To Ruoth ma Nyasach chunje mag jonabi, nooro malaikane mondo onyis jotichne gik mabiro timore mapiyo.” 
\s1 Biro mar Yesu 
\p  
\v 7 \wj “Neuru abiro mapiyo! Ngʼatno en ngʼat mogwedhi momako weche mokor manie kitabuni!”\wj* 
\b  
\p  
\v 8 An, Johana ema nawinjo gigi kendo ne anenogi. To kane asewinjogi kendo nenogi, napodho piny e tiend malaika mane nyisagi.  
\v 9 To nokwera kowachona niya, “Kik itim kamano. An bende an jatich wadu matiyo kodi kaachiel gi joweteni ma jonabi gi jogo duto morito weche manie kitabuni. Mi Nyasaye duongʼ!” 
\p  
\v 10 Bangʼ mano nowachona niya, “Kik ilingʼ mak ihulo weche mokor manie kitabuni, nikech kindeno ma gigo onego timre chiegni.  
\v 11 We ngʼat matimo richo odhi nyime kod timo richo; kendo ngʼat ma chunye ochido odhi nyime timo timbe mochido; to ngʼat matimo tim makare bende odhi nyime gi timo tim makare, to ngʼat maler odhi nyime gibedo maler.” 
\b  
\p  
\v 12 \wj “Ne! Abiro piyo! Atingʼo michna, to abiro miyo ngʼato ka ngʼato kaluwore kod gima osetimo.\wj* 
\v 13 \wj An e Alfa gi Omega, tiende ni Jal Mokwongo kendo Mogik kendo An e Chakruok gi Giko.\wj* 
\b  
\p  
\v 14 \wj “Jogo gin joma ogwedhi ma oseluoko kandhogi maler, mondo omi gibed gi ratiro mar chamo olemb yath mar ngimano kendo gikadh ka gidonjo e dhorangeye mag dalano.\wj* 
\v 15 \wj To jogo ma timbegi richo, gi jojuogi, gi joma terore kod jonek, gi joma lamo nyiseche manono kod ji duto ma ohero miriambo kendo matimo gik ma ok adiera, duto nobed oko.\wj* 
\b  
\p  
\v 16 \wj “An, Yesu aseoro malaikana mondo ohulni wechegi ikonygo kanise. An nyakwar Daudi bende an Sulwe Maler mar Okinyi.”\wj* 
\b  
\p  
\v 17 Roho gi miaha wacho niya, “Bi!” To ngʼat mowinjo, bende owach niya, “Bi!” Ngʼama riyo oloyo, mondo obi, kendo ngʼat mohero, mondo obi oyud pi ngima mochiw nono. 
\b  
\p  
\v 18 An Johana asiemo ngʼato ka ngʼato mawinjo wechegi mokor mag kitabuni kama: Ka ngʼato moro nomed wach moro amora kuom wechegi, Nyasaye nomedne ngʼatno masiche mondik e kitabuni.  
\v 19 To bende ka ngʼato moro nogol oko weche mokor manie kitabuni, Nyasaye nogol kuome kamaye pokne manie yath mar ngima kendo manie Dala Maduongʼ Maler, mondiki e kitabuni. 
\b  
\p  
\v 20 Jal manyiso wechegi duto wacho niya, \wj “Ee, abiro mapiyo.”\wj* 
\p Amin! Bi, Ruoth Yesu. 
\b  
\p  
\v 21 Ngʼwono mar Ruodhwa Yesu Kristo obed gi jo-Nyasaye. Amin.